    "name": "Lapidate [Air Savant]",
    "type": "spell",
    "img": "icons/weapons/thrown/bolas-stone.webp",
    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You pick up an object or a small creature. You shake it, saying a few words to animate it, and then throw it at your target. Your magic aids your aim and allows you to strike with unnatural force.</em></p><div data-draftjs-conductor-fragment=\"{\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap\"><p><span style=\"font-family:Signika, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Spell Attack</strong></span></p><p>You pick up a small object or a creature you are &amp;reference[grappled]{grappling} which is at least two sizes smaller than you. You throw it at a creature or location up to 60 ft. away.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Hit</strong>:\u00a0Target takes [[/damage 1d10 bludgeoning]] damage* and the thrown object or creature takes the same damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Miss</strong>:\u00a0Thrown object or creatures takes\u00a0[[/damage 1d10 bludgeoning]] damage*.</p><p></p></li></ul><p>*<strong>At Higher Levels</strong>: This spell's damage increases by [[/damage 1d10 bludgeoning]]{1d10} when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level ([[/damage 2d10 bludgeoning]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d10 bludgeoning]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d10 bludgeoning]]).</p><p></p></div><p><em style=\"font-style:italic\">An object or creature thrown by this spell does not take damage from falling, as the spell magically throttles the speed to the same speed constantly. If a creature is thrown 60 ft. into the air and then falls, they take this spell's damage when they hit the ground and no falling damage.</em></p>",
            "chat": ""
        },
